data.description: HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT! A rare find in Sun City Center that offers the Florida retirement lifestyle at its finest! This masterpiece is 1735 sq ft, 2 bed/2bath with a bonus den, and two-car garage.  Updates, Updates, Updates! Gives you a sence of appreciation when a home is truly move-in ready! The owner spared no expense as some of the updates include: Plantation shutters throughout the home, crown molding, luxury vinyl plank flooring, new AC filter system. In the kitchen there are 42” soft close cabinets, and new appliances with brushed brass finishes!. Appreciate the open floor plan that includes a formal dining and living room which is great for entertaining guests and spending quality time. The master bedroom and en suite includes dual vanities, newly updated shower, and a California Closet that is simply impressive! Although listed as a 2 bedroom, there is a den that can easily be converted into a 3rd bedroom or even an office. The two car garage has additional space for a golf cart. Enjoy piece of mind knowing you are in the gated community of Verona in Sun City Center. Access to the 24 hour fitness center, community pools, restaurants, landscaping, and many other features of the HOA. Also, you have access to Renaissance Club when you purchase the required club membership. Make your appointment today as this will not last long!
